hadiths[62]{hadithnumber,text}:
1783,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen bheja to farmaya : tum ehle-kitab logon key paas ja rahey ho to (sab sey pehley) unhen is baat ki dawat dena ke wo gawahi den ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin aur ye ke main (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) Allah ka Rasool hun. agar wo tumhari ye dawat qubul kar lein (aur Islam mein dakhil ho jaeyn) to unhen batao ke Allah Taala ney un par har din raat mein paanch namazein farz ki hain. agar wo tumhari ye baat taslim kar lein to phir unhen batao ke Allah ney un par unkey maalon mein sadqa farz kiya hai jo unkey dolat mand afrad sey liya jaeyga aur wapis unhi key naadaaron (ghareebon) ko dey diya jaeyga. agar wo tumhari ye baat bhi maan lein to unkey umda maal leney sey ijtinab (bacha) karna aur mazloom ki bad dua sey bach kar rehna kyonkey uskey aur Allah key darmiyan koi rukawat nahin.
1784,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ki zakat ada nahin karta , qiyamat key din uskey maal ko ganjey sanp ki shakal di jaeygi yahan tak key wo uski gardan mein toq bin kar lipat jaeyga. uskey baad Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Quran Majeed sey uski taeed mein ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (وَلَا يَحْسَبَنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ يَبْخَلُونَ بِمَآ ءَاتَىٰهُمُ ٱللَّهُ مِن فَضْلِهِ . . ۔) (Aale-Imran 3: 180 ) ''jinhen Allah Taala ney apney Fazal sey kuchh diya hai, wo us main apni kanjusi ko apney liye behtar khayal na karen balke wo unkey liye intehai bura hai. anqarib qiyamat key din unhen un ki kanjusi ki chiz key toq daley jaeyngey.''"
1785,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : oonton , bakriyon ya gaayon ka jo Malik un ki zakat ada nahin karta, (uskey ye janwer) qiyamat key din intehai badey aur motey ho kar ayengey, wo usey seengon sey maarengey aur paon sey rondengey, jab aakhiri janwer guzar chukengey to pehley guzar janey waley dobara aa jaeyngey. (usey yehi azab hota rahega) yahan tak key (sab) logon ka faisla ho jaeyga."
1786,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo oont jinka haq (zakat) ada nahin kya gaya, (qiyamat key din) aayengey, apney Malik ko paon sey rondengey, gaayen aur bakriyan aayengi, (wo bhi) apney Malik ko sumon sey rondengi aur seengon sey maarengi. aur khazana ganjaa sanp bin kar aa jaeyga. wo qiyamat ko jab apney Malik sey milega to Malik us sey do dafa bhageyga, phir wo (saanp) samney sey aayega to Malik (phir) bhageyga (aur) kaheyga : to kyon merey peechhey pad gaya hai? wo kaheyga : main tera khazana hun, main tera khazana hun. wo us sey bachney key liye uski taraf haath kerega to wo us (haath) ko apney munh mein ley ley ga."
1787,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Khalid bin Aslam (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath bahar gaya. unhen eik baddoo mila, usney kaha : Allah Taala ka irshad hai : (وَٱلَّذِينَ يَكْنِزُونَ ٱلذَّهَبَ وَٱلْفِضَّةَ وَلَا يُنفِقُونَهَا فِى سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ), ''jo log sona chaandi jama kartey hain aur usey Allah ki raah mein kharch nahin kartey . . .."" (is aayat ka kya matlab hai)? Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney isey kaha : jisney usey jama kya aur uski zakat ada na ki uskey liye tabahi hai. ye hukm zakat ka hukm nazil honey sey pehley tha jab zakat ka hukm nazil ho gaya to Allah ney isey maalon ki pakizgi ka zariya bana diya. phir mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : mujhey parwah nahin ke merey paas uhad pahad key barabar sona ho jiski tadaad (aur miqdaar) ka mujhey ilm ho aur uski zakat ada karun aur us sey Allah ki farma bradri waley kaam anjam dun."
1788,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tu ney apney maal ki zakat ada kar di to apney farz sey subuk-dosh (azaad) ho gaya."
1789,"Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : zakat key siwa maal mein koi haq nahin (jis ka ada karna Malik par farz ho)."
1790,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhen ghodon aur ghulamon ka sadqa maaf kar diya hai lekin (naqdi mein sey) chaliswan hissa ada karo, yani har chaalis dirham mein sey eik dirham."
1791,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr aur Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anhu sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) har bees Dinar ya (us sey kuchh) ziyada, main sey aadha Dinar aur chaalis Dinar mein sey eik Dinar wasul farmatey they."
1792,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, wo farmaati hain : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : kisi maal mein zakat nahin yahan tak key is par saal guzar jaey."
1793,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna : paanch wasq khajuron sey kam mein zakat nahin, paanch auqiya (chaandi) sey kam mein zakat nahin aur paanch sey kam oonton mein bhi nahin."
1794,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch sey kam oonton mein zakat nahin, paanch auqiya sey kam (chaandi) mein zakat nahin, paanch wasq sey kam (ghalley) mein zakat nahin."
1795,Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney wajib honey sey pehley jaldi kartey huye zakat ada karney ki ijazat maangi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ijazat dey di.
1796,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab koi shakhs Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein apney maal ka sadqa (zakat) ley kar hazir hota to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us ko dua detey. main apney maal ki zakat ley kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to aap ney farmaya : aey Allah ! Abu Oofaa key khandan par rehmat nazil farma."
1797,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum zakat do to uska sawab (hasil honey ki dua karna) farmosh na karo. yun kaho : (اللَّهُمَّ اجْعَلْهَا مَغْنَمًا , وَلَا تَجْعَلْهَا مَغْرَمًا), ''aey Allah ! isey faaedey ki chiz bana aur tawaan (jurmaana) na banana.''"
1798,"Imam ibne Shahab Zohri ney Salim bin Abdullah aur unkey walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma)) key wastey sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya : mujhey Hazrat Salim (Rahimahullah) ney wo tehreer padhwaai jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney zakat key barey mein wafat sey pehley likhwaai thi. mainey is mein ye baaten (likhi hui) paeen : paanch oonton par eik bakri (zakat) hai, das oonton par do bakriyan, pandarah oonton par teen bakriyan, bees oonton par chaar bakriyan hain, pachchees sey paintees par eik saal ki eik oontni hai. agar eik saala oontni na miley to do saala muzakkir oont hai. agar paintees sey eik oont bhi ziyada ho to un par do saala oontni hai. paintaalees tak (yehi zakat hai). agar pentaalis sey eik ziyada ho to (chhiyaalees sey) saath (60) tak teen saala oontni hai. agar (galley ki tadaad) saath (60) sey eik ziyada ho to pachhattar tak chaar saala oontni hai. agar pachhattar sey eik bhi zayed ho to nawwey tak un mein do saala do oontniyaan zakat hai. agar nawwey sey eik bhi ziyada ho to eik so bees tak teen teen saal ki do oontniyaan hain. agar (oont) is sey ziyada hon to har pachas mein teen saala oontni aur har chaalis mein do saala oontni hai."
1799,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch sey kam oonton par zakat farz nahin. chaar oonton par bhi kuchh (zakat) nahin. agar in ki tadaad paanch tak pahunch jaey to nau adad tak eik bakri (zakat) hai. agar wo das ho jaeyn to un mein chaudah ki tadaad tak do bakriyan hain. agar wo pandarah ho jaeyn to unnis ki tadaad tak teen bakriyan (zakat) hain. agar bees ho jaeyn to chobis honey tak chaar bakriyan hain. agar wo pachchees ki tadaad ko pahunch jaeyn to (pachchees sey) paintis tak eik saal ki eik oontni hai. agar eik saal ki oontni (rewad mein mojud) na ho to do saal ka muzakkir oont (ada kar dey). agar (paintis sey) eik oont ziyada ho to un mein paintaalees ki tadaad honey tak do saala eik oontni hai. agar (paintaalees sey) eik oont ziyada ho to un mein teen saala oontni (zakat) hai, saath (60) tak (yehi hukm hai). agar (saath (60) sey) eik oont ziyada ho to pachhattar tak chaar saala oontni hai. agar eik oont ziyada ho to nawwey ki tadaad tak do do saal ki do oontniyaan (wajib) hain. eik sau bees tak (yehi zakat hai). iskey baad har pachas mein teen saala oontni aur har chaalis mein do saala oontni hai."
1800,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney unkey liye ye tehreer likhi : بسم اللہ الرحمٰن الرحیم ye sadqey ka wo fariza hai jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon par muqarrar farmaya jiska Allah Taala ney apney Rasool ko hukm diya . janweron ki zakat mein oonton ki umaron key barey mein (ye hukm hai ke) jiskey oonton ki tadaad us had tak pahunch jaey ke is par Juzaa (chaar saala) ki adaegi farz ho lekin uskey paas (rewad mein) Juzaa mojud na ho, albatta hiqa (teen saala) mojud ho to us sey hiqa hi ley liya jaey. uskey sath agar uskey paas bakriyan hon to do bakriyan dey dey ya bees dirham dey dey. jis key paas oonton ki tadaad hiqa wasul karney ki had ko pahunchti ho aur uskey paas hiqa (teen saala) na ho balke uskey paas sirf binte-labun (do saala) mojud ho to us sey binte-labun hi qubul kar li jaey aur uskey sath us sey do bakriyan ya bees dirham ley liye jaeyn. jiski zakat binte-labun (do saala) ki had ko pahunchti ho aur wo uskey paas mojud na ho balke uskey paas hiqa (teen saala) mojud ho to us sey hiqa wasul kar liya jaey aur zakat jama karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan dey dey. aur jiski zakat binte-labun (do saala) ki had ko pahunchti ho, aur wo uskey paas mojud na ho balke uskey paas bint makhaz (eik saala) ho to us sey binte-makhaz qubul kar li jaey, aur wo uskey sath bees dirham ya do bakriyan ada kerey. jiski zakat binte-makhaz (eik saala muannas) ki had ko pahunchti ho, aur wo uskey paas na ho, albatta uskey paas binte-labun (do saala muannas) mojud ho to us sey binte-labun wasul kar li jaey aur zakat jama karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan ada kerey. jis key paas sahih adaegi key liye binte-makhaz (eik saala muannas) na ho lekin muzakkar ibne-labun (do saala muzakkar) mojud ho to us sey wohi wasul kar liya jaeyga aur uskey sath kuch bhi (lena dena) nahin hoga ."
1801,"Hazrat Suwed bin Ghafala (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hamarey paas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka aamil ( zakat wasul karney wala) aaya . mainey uska haath pakda aur uskey hukm namey mein padha : sadqey key dar sey alag alag rewadon ko jama na kya jaey aur na ikhattey rewad ko alag alag kya jaey . eik aadmi eik moti tazi badi si oontni ley kar hazir huwa, unhoney usey leney sey inkar kar diya to wo us sey kam darjey ki eik aur oontni ley aaya, unhoney wo ley li aur farmaya : mujhey kon si zamin sahara degi? aur kon sa aasman mujh par saya kerega agar main kisi musalman key behtareen oont wasul kar key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hunga?"
1802,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zakat wasul karney wala tumharey paas sey khush ho kar wapis jaey ."
1803,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Yamen bheja aur mujhey hukm diya ke main gaayon mein har chaalis mein sey eik do daant wali (gaey ya bail) aur har tees mein sey eik saal ka eik bachhda ya bachhdi wasul karun ."
1804,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har tees gaayon main eik saala bachda ya bachhdi (zakat) hai, aur chaalis par do daant ka (do saala janwer)."
1805,"Imam ibn Shahab Zohri (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Salim aur Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key wastey sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya : mujhey Hazrat Salim (Rahimahullah) ney wo dastawez padhwaai jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney faut honey sey pehley zakat key barey mein tehreer farmaai thi . (Imam Zohri farmatey hain) mujhey us dastawez mein ye ibarat likhi hui mili : chaalis sey eik so bees bakriyon tak eik bakri (zakat) hai. agar eik bhi ziyada ho jaey to (eik so ikkis sey ley kar) do so tak do bakriyan (wajibul-adaa) hain. agar un main eik bhi ziyada ho to (do so eik sey ley kar) teen so tak teen bakriyan hain. agar us sey ziyada hon to har so par eik bakri hai. mainey is mein ye ( hukm) bhi paya : alag alag ( rewadon) ko jama na kya jaey aur ikhattey ( eik) rewad ko alag alag na kya jaey . aur mujhey is mein ye ( hukm ( bhi) likha huwa) mila : zakat mein saand wasul kya jaey, na boodha janwer aur na aeb daar janwer ."
1806,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalmanon ( key janweron) ki zakat pani pilaney ki jagah wasul ki jaey."
1807,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaalis bakriyon main eik bakri ( zakat) hai, eik so bees tak ( yehi hukm hai.) agar eik ziyada ho jaey to do bakriyan hain, do so tak . agar ( do so sey) eik bakri ziyada ho to teen so tak teen bakriyan hain. agar us sey ziyada hon to har so main eik bakri ( zakat) hai. zakat key dar sey ikhattey ( rewad) ko alag alag na kya jaey, aur alag-alag ( rewadon ) ko ikhatta na kya jaey. aur rewad mein shareek do afrad barabari ki buniyadi par eik doosrey sey hisab kitab kar lein. aur zakat wasul karney waley ( aamil) ko boodha ya aeb daar janwer na diya jaey aur na saand diya jaey, illa ye ke zakat deney wala chahey."
1808,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zakat key mamley mein ziyadti karney wala zakat rok leney waley ki tarah hai."
1809,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna : aap farma rahey they : haq key sath zakat wasul karney wala , Allah ki raah mein jang karney waley ki tarah hai yahan tak key ghar wapis aa jaey ."
1810,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Unais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik din Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey zakat key masley par un ki baat cheet hui . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kya aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko zakat mein khayanat ka zikr kartey huye ye farmatey nahin suna : jo koi is mein sey eik oont ya eik bakri ki khayanat kerega, qiyamat key din usey apney ooper laadey huye hazir hoga ? , 'Hazrat Abdullah bin Unais (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan ( suni hai.)"
1811,"Hazrat Ibrahim bin Ata apney walid Ata bin Abu-Memuna sey riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) ko zakat wasul karney par muqarrar kya gaya. jab wo (apney faraaiz anjam deney key baad) wapis (Madina) aaye to unhen kaha gaya : maal kahan hai? unhoney farmaya : kya aap ney mujhey maal laney key liye bheja tha? hamney wahin sey wasul kya jahan sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein wasul kya kartey they, aur wahin dey diya jahan ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein) diya kartey they."
1812,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman par uskey ghulam mein aur uskey ghodey mein sadqa nahin hai.
1813,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhen ghodon aur ghulamon ki zakat maaf kar di hai."
1814,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen (governer bana kar) Yamen rawana kya aur un sey farmaya : ghalley mein sey ghalla wasul karna, bakriyon sey bakri, oonton mein sey oont, aur gaayon mein sey gaey ."
1815,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un paanch chizon ki zakat ka hukm jari farmaya hai : gehun, jo, khajoor, munaqqa aur makai."
1816,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo khetiyan barish aur chashmon sey sairab hon, un mein daswan hissa hai aur jisey pani khinch kar diya jaey, is mein beeswaan hissa (zakat) hai."
1817,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : jisey barish , nadiyon aur chashmon sey pani miley , ya jo zamin ki nami sey sairab ho, is mein daswaan hissa hai, aur jisey janweron par pani la kar seencha jaey, is mein beeswan hissa hai."
1818,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey Yamen bheja aur mujhey hukm diya ke main barish sey sairab honey wali (Zarai pedawar) sey aur nami sey sairab honey wali (pedawar) sey daswaan hissey wasul karun aur jisey aalaat key zariey sey (kunwen waghera sey) nikal kar pani diya jaey, is mein sey beeswaan hissa wasul karun. Imam Yahya bin Adam (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Baal Ashri Azi, un alfaz ka matlab, 'barish sey sairab honey wali hai.' khas tor par Ashri us fasal ko kehtey hain jo sirf badal aur barish sey sairab ho, usey barish key ilawa koi pani na miley, aur Baal angoor ki un bailon ko kehtey hain jinki judein satah zamin key nichey pani tak ja pahunchein, unhen pani deney ki zarurat nahin hoti , unhen paanch chhe saal tak bhi pani na diya jaey to bardasht kar leti hain to ye chiz baal kehlaati hai. sail (sailab) wadi mein beh kar aaney waley pani ko kehtey hain. aur Ghail (adna sailab) bhi sailab hi hota hai lekin wo sail sey kam hota hai."
1819,Hazrat itaab bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon key paas aadmi bhejtey they to wo unkey angooron aur phalon (ki miqdaar) ka andaza lagata tha.
1820,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar Fateh kya to un sey ye tey kya ke zamin aur tamam sona chaandi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka hoga. khaibar walon ney kaha : hum log zamin (ki kaasht aur dekh bhaal) sey ziyada waqif hain to ye zamin hamen (kaasht key liye) us shart par dey dijiye ke hum is mein (kheti ka) kaam karen aur phalon ka nisf hamara ho, nisf tumhara. Raavi bayan kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen us shart par wo zamin dey di. jab khajhuron key phal utaarney ka waqt aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko unkey paas bheja. unhoney kajhooron (key phal) ka andaza lagaya , Madiney waley andaza laganey ko Khars kehtey they, aur farmaya is baagh main itna phal hai. unhoney kaha : ibne-Rawaha! aap ney (sahih miqdaar sey) ziyada andaza lagaya hai. unhoney farmaya : tab main khajuron ka andaza laga kar jo miqdaar mutaiyan karta hun uska nisf tumhen dey dunga. unhon (yahudiyon) ney kaha : yehi haq hai, usi par aasman aur zamin qaaim hain. aur kaha : hum itna hi leney par razi hain jitna aap kehtey hain."
1821,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghar sey masjid mein) tashrif laye (to dekha ke) kisi aadmi ney (khajoor key) khoshey ya eik khosha (masjid mein) latka diya tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key haath main eik chhadi thi. aap us khoshay ko khat khat chhadi maarney lagey. aur aap farma rahey they is sadqey wala chahta to us sey behtar sadqa dey sakta tha. us sadqey ka Malik qiyamat key din nikammi khajuren hi khayega."
1822,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney us aayat mubarka ki tafseer kartey huye farmaya : ( وَمِمَّآ أَخْرجْنَا لَكُم مِّنَ ٱلْأَرضِ , وَلَا تَيَمَّمُوا۟ ٱلْخَبِيثَ مِنْهُ تُنفِقُونَ ) (2 : 267 ) aur jo cheezen hamney tumharey liye zamin sey nikali hain, un mein sey (Allah ki raah mein kharch karo) aur nikammi cheezen kharch karney ka qasd (irada) na karo. unhoney farmaya : ye aayat ansaar key barey mein nazil hui. ansaar ki aadat thi ke jab khajur key darakhton ka phal utara jata to wo apney baaghon sey khajuron key chand khoshey (sadqey key tor par) nikaltey aur in ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid mein do sutunon key darmiyan eik rassi par latka detey. nadaar Muhajir un mein sey) hasbe-zarurat (kha letey.) baaz oqaat (koi aadmi un mein nikammi khajuron ka khosha bhi shamil kar deta aur ye khayal karta ke itney bahut sey rakhey janey waley khoshon mein uska ye khosha deney sey bhi guzaara ho jaeyga. jin afrad ney aisa kya tha unkey barey mein ye aayat nazil hui : ( وَلَا تَيَمَّمُوا۟ ٱلْخَبِيثَ مِنْهُ تُنفِقُونَ )' nikammi chiz ka qasd (irada) na karo ke is mein sey tum kharch kartey ho. yani nikammi khajuren deney ka qasd (irada) na karo. ( وَلَسْتُم بِـَٔاخِذِيهِ إِلَّآ أَن تُغْمِضُوا۟ فِيهِ ) aur tum khud unhen nahin letey siwaye uskey ke chashm poshi kar lo. yani agar wo khajuren tumhen tohfey key tor par di jaeyn to tum unhen qubul nahin karogey siwaye us ke ke deney waley ki sharam sey qubul kar lo. tumhen ye narazi mehsus hogi ke usney tumhen (tohfa mein) wo chiz bheji hai jo tumharey kaam ki nahin. (isliye) tumhen malum hona chahiye ke Allah Taala tumharey sadqaat sey be niaz hai."
1823,"Hazrat Abu Sayyara Mutai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kya aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas shehad ki makkhiyaan hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : daswaan hissa (zakat) ada karo. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! unhen merey liye khas kar dijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wo merey liye khas kar den."
1824,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney shehad ka ushr wasul kya.
1825,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqa fitr key tor par eik saa khajoor ya eik saa jo deney ka hukm diya . Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : phir logon ney do mudd gehun ko uskey barabar qarar dey liya .
1826,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon mein sey har azad , ghulam , mard aur aurat par (fi kas) eik saa jo ya eik saa khajuren sadqa fitr muqarrar farmaya."
1827,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney rozey ko laghw aur na munasib baaton (key gunah) sey pak karney key liye aur miskinon ko khana khilaney key liye sadqae-fitr muqarrar farmaya. jisney namaz (eid) sey pehley ye ada kar diya, uska ye qubul shuda sadqa hai aur jisney namaz key baad ada kya to wo to eik aam sadqa hai (sadqa fitr nahin.)"
1828,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : zakat ka hukm nazil honey sey pehley Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen sadqa fitr ada karney ka hukm diya tha. jab zakat key ehkam nazil ho gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen sadqa fitr ka ( dobara) hukm nahin diya aur mana bhi nahin farmaya , albatta hum log uski adaegi kartey hain."
1829,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey darmiyan mojud they to hum sadqa fitr key tor par eik saa ghalla, eik saa khushk khajuren, eik saa jo, eik saa paneer ya eik saa munaqqa ada kya kartey they. hum usi tareeqe-kaar par amal kartey rahey yahan tak key Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) hum logon key paas Madina Munawra mein aaye. unhoney logon sey jo khitab farmaya is mein ye bhi kaha : merey khayal main to Sham ki gehun key do mudd un chizon key eik saa key barabar hain. chunanche logon ney us (qol) par amal karna shuru kar diya . Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main to jab tak zinda hun, hamesha isi tarah (pura saa) ada karta rahunga jis tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak mein kya karta tha."
1830,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan Hazrat Saad al-Qurz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik saa khushk khajoor ya eik saa jo ya eik saa salat (eik qism key jo) sadqa fitr ada karney ka hukm diya .
1831,"Hazrat Alaa bin Hazrami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Bahrin ya Hijr (zakat wasul karney key liye ( bheja .) baaz oqaat) main eik baagh mein pahunchta jo kaee bhaiyon ki mushtarka milkiyat hota jin mein eik bhai musalman hota to main musalman sey ushr wasul karta aur mushrik sey khiraaj ."
1832,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney marfooan bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wasq saath saa ka hota hai.
1833,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wasq saath saa ka hota hai."
1834,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Zenab Saqfiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kya : kya meri janib sey apney khawind par aur apney zer kafalat yatimon par kharch karna, sadqey key tor par kafi ho sakta hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is khatoon ko do sawab milengey, sadqa karney ka sawab aur rishtey daaron ( sey neki) ka sawab. eik dusri sanad sey bhi Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki zauja mohtarma sey isi tarah marvi hai."
1835,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen sadqa karney ka hukm diya . Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kya : kya merey liye ye sadqa kafi (aur durust) hoga ke main apney khawind ko sadqa dey dun kyonkey wo nadaar hain aur apney yatim bhatijon ko dey dun aur main unka falan falan kharch bardasht karti hun aur har haal mein (un sey maali taawun karti hun .) Raavi ney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan . Raavi ney kaha : Zenab (Raziallahu anha) haathon sey kaam karney wali (hunar mand khatoon) thin ."
1836,"Hazrat Hisham bin Urwa apney walid Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey aur wo Hisham key dada (Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka rassi ley kar pahad par jana, aur (wahan sey) endhan ka gathaa apni peeth par (utha kar) lana, usey bech kar uski qeemat par qanaa'at karna, is baat sey behtar hai ke logon sey maangta phirey, wo usey kuchh den ya na den."
1837,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kon meri eik baat (par pabandi sey amal kerney) ka zimma uthata hai, main usey jannat ka zimma deta hun? mainey kaha : main (ye zimme-daari qubul karta hun). aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon sey kuchh na maangna. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed (Rahimahullah) ney bayan farmaya : Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sawari par hotey aur koda (haath sey) gir jata to kisi sey na kehtey they ke ye pakdaana balke khud utar kar pakad letey they."
1838,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs maal mein izafa karney key liye logon sey un ki dolat maangta hai wo to jahannam key angaaron ka sawal kar raha hai. (usey ikhtiyar hai ke) kam talab karey ya ziyada mang ley."
1839,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sadqa na maal daar key liye halal hai, aur na taqatwar tandurust aadmi key liye."
1840,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key paas itna kuchh tha ke usey (sawal sey) mustaghni (be-niyaaz) kar dey, phir bhi usney sawal kya to qiyamat key din uska sawal uskey chehrey mein khraashon aur zakhmon ki surat mein zahir hoga. arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kitna maal usey ghani qarar dilwa sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pachas dirham ya itni qeemat ka sona. eik aadmi ney Sufiyan sey kaha ke Shoba to Hakim bin Juber sey bayan nahin kartey to Sufiyan ney kaha ke hamein ye hadees Zubeda ney Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed key wastey sey bayan ki hai."
1841,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch afrad key ilawa kisi ameer aadmi key liye sadqa (aur zakat) khana halal nahin.(1) sadqa wasul karney wala (sarkari mulaazim). (2) Allah ki raah mein jang karney wala (Mujahid). (3) wo dolat mand jo sadqey ki chiz apney maal key badley kharid leta hai. (4) ya (ye surat ke) kisi faqir ko sadqa diya gaya aur usney wo kisi ghani ko tohfe key taur par dey diya. (5) diwaaliya (maqrooz)."
1842,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo koi pak chiz ka sadqa karta hai, aur Allah Taala pak (halal aur umda) chiz hi qubul karta hai, to Rehmaan usey apney daain haath mein ley leta hai, agar-che eik khajoor hi ho. wo Rahmaan key haath mein badhti jati hai yahan tak key pahad sey badi ho jati hai. wo us chiz ko is (sadqa deney waley) key liye is tarah paaltaa hai jis tarah tum mein sey koi apney bachhedey ko, ya oont ya gaaey key bachchey ko paaltaa hai."
1843,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim Taai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey har shakhs key sath Allah Taala kalam farmaeyga jabke bandey aur Rab key darmiyan koi tarjamaan nahin hoga. banda samney nazar uthaeyga to usey samney aag nazar aayegi, daain taraf dekhega to apney bhejey huye aemaal (kaam) hi nazar aayengey, baain taraf dekhega to (udhar bhi) apney bhejey huye aamaal (kaam) hi nazar aayengey, lihaza jo shakhs aag sey bachney key liye aadhi khajoor hi dey sakta hai (ziyada ki taqat nahin), wo yehi kar ley."
1844,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir Zabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : miskeen ko sadqa dena sadqa hai, aur rishtey daaron ko (sadqa dena) do nekiyan hain : sadqa bhi, aur sila rehmi bhi."
